Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.55,0:01:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是属于他的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于他来说最好的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.33,0:01:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能使他安心的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:01:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对小月来说也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.63,0:02:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎 欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.74,0:02:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋刀鱼 一条30日元 两条50日元
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来点吗 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.35,0:02:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多送给小姑娘一条
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃些 早点长大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里“球棒少年”是不会出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只会保护小月的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:03:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为麻洛美已经不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把麻洛美拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在全国突然出现的神秘黑色物质
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,势力正急剧扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并席卷各地 造成重大损失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无法阻止它的成长了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹭月子 你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 月子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:03:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHO-P
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终回。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你SHO-P
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲怎能只给自己买香烟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香烟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.22,0:04:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还是没戒掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吸MILD SEVEN来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.03,0:05:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组长 能听到吗 组长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吧 组长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和月子在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马庭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 把月子还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去麻洛美后的人们内心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使“球棒少年”无限成长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打倒那家伙 一定要鹭月子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗 组长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻洛美和“球棒少年”一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们的根源都是月子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻洛美原本是月子的小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是由于月子不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天把麻洛美…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么“球棒少年”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西根本不会出现在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:05:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察先生把有害电波消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是警察 真是为咱老百姓办实事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱布
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血压下降
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输血 赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 她不可能在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 再来一杯啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不要多喝为好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱啊 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长得不像老爹 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来一定是日本第一的大美人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啤酒来了 让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赠送的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作很累吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了猪狩先生最喜欢的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美佐江
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美 快来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在那儿那么亲热
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美佐江
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是心有点慌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你会晚回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎样进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把老公还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是你应该存在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月 快带父亲逃跑 快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 老公
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么会跟来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 麻洛美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉强自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庙会 工作本来就很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是两回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我想有个女儿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直和老爸相处不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想和自己的儿子也那样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪吗 我说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 孩子 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受现实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你在身边就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我不在了 就不用这么痛苦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许再说那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是想逃避罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为逃避就能得救的想法只是幻想而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有多痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要正视现实 并一起熬过去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美佐江
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 想和你道别
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我非常熟悉的你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 非常明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美佐江
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心肺停止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心脏按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是你的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 我当然明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界满是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个个都这么胡闹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 这里可是属于你的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的世界会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗不要总说个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的归宿早就不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去归宿的现实才是我真正的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组长回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马庭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉要AA制了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是因为月子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“球棒少年”是月子十年前制造出来的妄想的产物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她让那个东西在现代复活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令事态扩大到如此地步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错的是它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是“球棒少年”的错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清醒吧 麻洛美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的死是月子造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是小学生的你遭到道路魔的袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在带着宠物狗麻洛美散步的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿着溜冰鞋 手持金属球棒的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方的搜查也是一无所获
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有抓到犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为从一开始就根本不存在道路魔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你自己的不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松开了麻洛美的绳索
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果麻洛美被飞驰而过的汽车碾死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没敢告诉父亲这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你害怕被责骂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.83,0:14:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以编造了什么道路魔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了把自己装扮成受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的被打了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父亲全部都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他为了你 装作到处寻找犯人的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是因为他对你过分严厉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造成你性格内向 他很为此而自责
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 这里面包含着他对你的补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及对你能承认错误的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马庭 后面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算合为一体了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:15:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论你多么强大都是个骗局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洞察真相之剑的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马庭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.13,0:15:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来 快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别回头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 就因为一只狗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界还真不争气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的死是月子造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你自己的不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松开了麻洛美的绳索
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果麻洛美被飞驰而过的汽车碾死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没敢告诉父亲这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你害怕被责骂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以编造了什么道路魔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了把自己装扮成受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻洛美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻洛美 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.34,0:17:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了 麻洛美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才让父亲买给你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕父亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他的错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻洛美 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是 战后一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京都复兴实行委员会宣布重建完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京已经从两年前的悲剧中完全复兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.74,0:21:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说东京已经复兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我们公司还远没有复兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.65,0:21:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次以后 那个计划完全不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部是动画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一般的电影不同吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是唯独狗不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那主人可烦人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是忙得不可开交
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就没听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和芙雅一起呼噜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然这消息就给别家了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.92,0:24:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.22,0:24:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像快要结束的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.79,0:24:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮回过后又是开始
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.93,0:24:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捡起基石堆积起来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.93,0:24:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,循环往复的无限体
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.34,0:24:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有解不开的谜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.14,0:24:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解不开的迷没有答案
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.64,0:24:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.81,0:24:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
